f15c7d3bd05f38c32eacb94b26","tid":525872,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"85a71abd4456e09b8d4b9c0520d4602f3ffd85db","tid":525872,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69f257e29fef0e02be6f122e7ef197aac1170c6e","tid":525872,"uid":56874,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:15:01.000Z","msg":"丸尾末夫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/11/151400_75adb4ef317e3ebe0ca95b873323f688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2F151400_75adb4ef317e3ebe0ca95b873323f688.png&h=894a6b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n班長選舉票數大比數壓到小丸子當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T18:20:58.000Z","msg":"小丸子嘅直接對手係小渚隻肥閪喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n丸尾係同隔離嘅惠美須對撼呀<br />\n而且佢兩個一早話唔選先至贏到咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T20:32:55.000Z","msg":"唔洗咁認真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c83e3a68e8d444f68031c975c5deffeb416cb2f","tid":525872,"uid":86402,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e6c91d9f57def484adfe7bb500c89f737947545","tid":525872,"uid":22018,"like":69,"dislike":3,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:51:11.000Z","msg":"係雙方唔用任何法寶下，全盛時期既胖虎同出木杉聯手可唔可以打敗大雄？ <br />\n<br />\n胖虎同出木杉既強處相信大家都知所以唔講 <br />\n<br />\n以下講下大雄既能力 <br />\n神力：多啦A夢重129.3公斤，故事中大雄多次徒手抱，攬，推，甚至拖住多啦a夢飛奔 <br />\n<br />\n高速：多啦a夢最高速係129.3km/h , 大雄多次同多啦a夢逃跑時跑係多啦a夢前面，證明大雄奔跑既速度高於129.3km/h <br />\n<br />\n神反應：劇場版敵人多次近距離向大雄開槍都避得過，反應能力比neo仲高(neo都中過一槍) <br />\n<br />\n高速運算能力：有集多啦a夢同佢回到古代，當地人講出當時既距離計算單位，大雄立即可以將該單位轉換成公里並計出身處地方同自家既距離，而且玩花繩亦需要大腦運算同手腳協調能力，大雄只要係電視睇一次就可以立即模仿 <br />\n<br />\n神學習能力：上面提及過玩花繩&hellip;仲有無論多複雜既法寶，只要多啦A夢講解一次就能運用自如，甚至會改良用法令多啦a夢一吃一驚 <br />\n<br />\n神記憶：只要出現過既法寶，大雄都可以講出名稱同埋用法 <br />\n<br />\n高速回復能力：無論比狗咬，比人打，甚至高處墮下搞到遍地鱗傷，只要數分鐘就可以恢復，印象中大雄亦未出入過醫院 <br />\n<br />\n快速睡眠：唔駛多講，都市人羡慕既能力 <br />\n<br />\n總括以上能力，加上多次拯救地球，宇宙，大雄係最接近神既男人，究極胖虎同出木杉聯手有無一分既勝算？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T20:36:06.000Z","msg":"漏咗射擊能力"},{"pid":"64dec16da28c9e2a0af26316e460309468b7e36f","tid":525872,"uid":120850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"火雲邪神"},{"pid":"2ba79b32f3755b31fb740260b8041bcd39bb0ff2","tid":525872,"uid":9643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:59:25.000Z","msg":"大和猛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5722fed03e7859e51a5563fd892e0f29f49813f3","tid":525872,"uid":98223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"小智仲未贏到聯賽"},{"pid":"4cb7a6757761d3296989bd59e6dc2ce7f8761915","tid":525872,"uid":159805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"比古清十郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061065a18c14018101f39dd5367e450fcea47620","tid":525872,"uid":103339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:15:29.000Z","msg":"噬謊者計打鬥嘅話全部都勁過主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd71032052212a4ba4081e73beabef0f3d5f3ca","tid":525872,"uid":100283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:23:42.000Z","msg":"超速搖搖北條院聖斗<br />\n浪客劍心比古清十郎<br />\n驚爆危機雷納德<br />\nKonoSuba任何人"},{"pid":"b406c8ac95d9a30d36e4bfd9769c433e9a3aedde","tid":525872,"uid":36341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"一輝"},{"pid":"245c8dca2366054ca802373f7ad11fd90ac7d37d","tid":525872,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"大撚把喎 樓豬係剩係睇過one punch man"},{"pid":"409da021d10978e32c0d55